    { question: "Can clients sign on their own phone before arriving?", answer: "Yes. Send a link in the booking confirmation or display a QR code at the door. Clients complete the waiver on their phone before they walk in." },
    { question: "How is InkFlow different from Waiverly or Smartwaiver?", answer: "Those are standalone waiver apps. InkFlow includes waivers, booking, payments, CRM, and aftercare in one platform — no integrations, no extra monthly fees." },
    { question: "Do you have parental consent forms for minors?", answer: "Yes. Built-in parental consent workflow. Minors waivers require a guardian e-signature and are stored separately for compliance." },
  ]} />
  <Navbar />

  <!-- HERO: GEO首句即答案 -->
  <section class="pt-24 pb-16 sm:pt-32">
