    <div class="mx-auto max-w-3xl px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
      <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-white text-center">Paper Waivers Cost You Time, Money, and Legal Risk</h2>
      <div class="mt-8 space-y-4">
        <div class="rounded-xl border border-ink-800 bg-ink-900/30 p-5"><h3 class="text-white font-semibold text-sm">Paper check-in takes 5 minutes per client — digital waivers cut that to 30 seconds.</h3><p class="mt-1 text-sm text-gray-400">Finding the right form, cleaning the iPad, waiting for handwritten signatures. Multiply by 10 clients a day and you've lost nearly an hour. InkFlow's QR check-in lets clients sign on their phone before they walk in.</p></div>
