            <h6 class="mt-2 text-sm font-medium text-gray-400">GDPR-Compliant Data Retention</h6>
            <p class="text-sm text-gray-400">Waivers are retained for the legally required period, then automatically purged. Clients can request waiver deletion with one click.</p>
            <h4 class="mt-3 text-lg font-semibold text-white">Vs Smartwaiver: Included at $0 vs $19-99/mo</h4>
